-- Merger of drugmakers Valeant, Actavis on hold: source
-- 
-- Sat Apr 27, 2013 4:18pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/04/27/us-valeant-actavis-idUSBRE93Q0CJ20130427

 

 (Reuters) - Talks are on hold to merge drugmakers Valeant Pharmaceuticals International Inc ( VRX.TO ) and Actavis Inc ( ACT.N ) in a deal that would have created a healthcare giant, a person familiar with the situation told Reuters on Saturday. 
 A Valeant ( VRX.N ) spokeswoman and an Actavis spokesman could not be immediately reached for comment outside of business hours. (Reporting by  Soyoung Kim  in New York; writing by Rod Nickel in Winnipeg, Manitoba)